msgid "Happy Clients"
msgstr "Zufriedene Kunden"

msgid ""
"Professional LED lighting systems for sports, industrial, and infrastructure"
" applications. Engineered in Beijing since 2007, trusted in 50+ countries "
"worldwide."
msgstr ""
"Professionelle LED-Beleuchtungssysteme für Sport, Industrie und "
"Infrastruktur. Entwickelt in Peking seit 2007, vertraut in über 50 Ländern "
"weltweit."

